                     <interp inst="t18470816-1961-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY.</hi> Aged 28.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury.</hi>
                  </rs>—
